dcterms:description: A corpus for Named Entity Recognition (NER) in Spanish biomedical texts, focusing on chemical and protein entities. It includes three entity types: normalizables, notnormalizables, and proteins. The corpus is divided into training, development, and test sets.
dcterms:title: PharmaCoNER
